### URL Shortener API - Testing with REST Client Extension

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### 2. Create Short URL with Auto-Generated Code
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/shorten
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "original_url": "https://github.com/anthropics/anthropic-sdk-python"
}

### 3. Create Short URL with Custom Code
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/shorten
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "original_url": "https://www.python.org",
  "custom_short_code": "py"
}

### 4. Create Another Custom Code
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/shorten
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "original_url": "https://github.com",
  "custom_short_code": "gh"
}

### 5. Lookup a Short Code
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/lookup/py

### 6. Lookup Non-Existent Code (Should Return 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/lookup/notexist

### 7. List All URLs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/all

### 8. Update a Short Code
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/update/py
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "original_url": "https://python.org/docs"
}

### 9. Verify Update
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/lookup/py

### 10. Delete a Short Code
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/delete/gh

### 11. Verify Deletion (Should Return 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/lookup/gh

### 12. List All Remaining URLs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/all

### 13. Error Test - Missing Required Field
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/shorten
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "original_url": ""
}

### 14. Error Test - Duplicate Short Code
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/shorten
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "original_url": "https://example.com",
  "custom_short_code": "py"
}
